data.description: Welcome to this expansive estate boasting the largest lot in coveted Fawn Lake, spanning over 15 acres of picturesque landscape, fully fenced for ultimate privacy and security. A grand 2-story front entry welcomes you with a sweeping curved staircase. Entertain with ease in the expansive formal dining room, complemented by a large custom butler's pantry perfect for hosting gatherings. A well-appointed study with an attached bath offers versatility for remote work or relaxation.  Past the front entryway you'll find a light-filled 2-story family room. With its vaulted ceiling and stunning stone fireplace, this space offers a grand yet inviting atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation. Indulge your culinary desires in the gourmet kitchen, complete with a Wolf stove and SubZero fridge. The large eating area, featuring another charming stone fireplace, provides a cozy ambiance for family meals and entertaining, while a wall of windows floods the space with natural light, creating a bright and airy environment. Step into the main level primary suite, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a private ensuite for your utmost comfort and relaxation. Convenience meets functionality with a second entrance featuring a mudroom, laundry area, and back stairs for seamless access. Upstairs, discover six generously sized bedrooms, including a bonus room equipped with sleep pods for added versatility and comfort. Notable enhancements include the addition of a new bedroom on the second floor, new carpet in the bedrooms, a new wine fridge in the butler’s pantry, and new HVAC unit (2020) for year-round comfort. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with white paint, offering a fresh and timeless aesthetic. The expansive basement of this remarkable estate, offers a haven of comfort and entertainment. Discover a sprawling bedroom suite complete with a walk-in closet and an upgraded bath, providing a serene retreat for guests or family members. Adjacent to the bedroom suite, is another versatile space perfect for an office or library, ideal for work or relaxation. Entertain in style in the expansive recreation room, offering endless possibilities for gatherings and leisure activities. Stay active and healthy in the home gym, equipped with all necessary equipment conveying with the property, ensuring your fitness needs are met right at home. Ample storage space is available in the huge storage room, providing organization and convenience. Experience unparalleled comfort with the upgraded geothermal heating/cooling system, offering energy-efficient climate control throughout the home. Escape to your private oasis outdoors, featuring an Anthony Sylvan saltwater custom pool with an upgraded pool house, complete with a chandelier, new flooring, special lighting, fan, Wi-Fi connectivity, and built-ins.  The rear of the home features a slate patio adorned with a wood-burning outside fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for al fresco gatherings and cozy evenings. Enjoy premium amenities including two 1500-gallon propane tanks, a surround sound system throughout the porch, backyard patio, and main floor of the house, as well as an irrigation system for effortless lawn maintenance. Take advantage of the ASSUMABLE  LOAN at a remarkable 2.85% interest rate, offering exceptional financial flexibility. Enjoy resort-style living within the prestigious gated community of Fawn Lake where fine dining meets convenience with community restaurants just steps away from your front door. The private lake is perfect for motorcraft activities such as skiing, stand-up paddleboarding, tubing, and fishing. Enjoy endless days of fun and relaxation on the water, creating cherished memories with family and friends. In addition to the waterfront activities, residents of Fawn Lake enjoy access to world-class recreational facilities, including tennis and pickleball courts, providing opportunities for friendly competition and fitness. Welcome home!
